name: UIPrinter.JobTypes
desc: Constants that indicate the types of jobs that the printer supports.

items.name: static var document: UIPrinter.JobTypes
items.desc: The printer supports standard document printing.

items.name: static var envelope: UIPrinter.JobTypes
items.desc: The printer supports printing on envelopes.

items.name: static var label: UIPrinter.JobTypes
items.desc: The printer supports printing on cut labels.

items.name: static var photo: UIPrinter.JobTypes
items.desc: The printer supports printing with photographic print quality.

items.name: static var receipt: UIPrinter.JobTypes
items.desc: The printer supports printing receipts on a continuous roll of paper.

items.name: static var roll: UIPrinter.JobTypes
items.desc: The printer supports printing documents or photos on a continuous roll of paper.

items.name: static var largeFormat: UIPrinter.JobTypes
items.desc: The printer supports printing larger than the ISO A3 size.

items.name: static var postcard: UIPrinter.JobTypes
items.desc: The printer supports printing on postcards.
